TITLE: Episode 22 - The Most Important Tech From the Last Ten Years
DESCRIPTION: The 2010s were a wild time. It's almost unbelievable how far tech has come in just ten years. In this episode, Thaddeus and Gary talk about the most important technological changes and advancements from over this last decade.
